<div class="prima-wrapper"><div data-prima="Text" aria-label="false"       style="position: relative;"><p dir="ltr" >The vulnerability detection script is intended for <a  href="https://access.redhat.com/product-life-cycles?product=Red%20Hat%20Enterprise%20Linux" >currently supported Red Hat Enterprise Linux versions</a>. The detection script can also be used with layered products on top of Red Hat Enterprise Linux where customers have access to run the script.</p><h2 dir="ltr" >Ansible Playbook</h2><p dir="ltr" >An Ansible playbook, CVE-2020-10713-update_fixit.yml, is provided below. This playbook updates all relevant packages. To use the playbook, specify the hosts you'd like to update with the HOSTS extra var:</p><p dir="ltr" >ansible-playbook -e HOSTS=&lt;myhosts&gt; CVE-2020-10713-update_fixit--2020-07-29-1613.yml</p><p dir="ltr" >To verify the legitimacy of the playbook, you can download the <a  href="https://access.redhat.com/sites/default/files/cve-2020-10713-update_fixit--2020-09-15-0907.yml.asc" >detached OpenPGP signature</a>.</p></div></div>
